WEBVTT FILE:

00:00:00.850 --> 00:00:05.920
there is a right tone, and the right tone involves respect in respect

00:00:05.920 --> 00:00:10.980
 goes both ways. Discounting a subordinate's concern is not respectful,

00:00:10.980 --> 00:00:16.050
 in the same token, demanding that a subordinate respect you. If for

00:00:16.050 --> 00:00:21.120
 no other reason than you are in the position you're in, it's important

00:00:21.120 --> 00:00:26.180
 to set that standard. You can't operate without it effectively.

